{"tid":1017693,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"梁釗鋒隻EP幾好聽 有冇機上到男歌手一線？","createTime":"2019-02-11T15:26:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T15:18:43.000Z","uid":205503,"like":19,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ec175cf7cb1a1f838983c196c92c3ac1c0a2947a","tid":1017693,"uid":205503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T15:26:59.000Z","msg":"聽咗歐美歌幾年，上年年尾見Eason 基仔 軒仔 Juno都出碟，開始聽返本地歌，<br />\n<br />\n播spotify啲canton playlist 聽到釗鋒單飛出歌，佢把聲本身都易認，<br />\n個range幾闊，高低音都正，又唔會太薄似中性聲，把聲幾撚型，但排行榜都排得幾後下。<br />\n之後我再search佢個名先知有出EP，幾首歌都唔錯，算係滄海遺珠。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n廢事貼link畀人話打手，有興趣自己spotify, apple music 搵。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n算啦貼一首，因為呢首係佢自己作曲填詞。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G53uVamqOd0&amp;list=PLxWYT0p5UiNeoAPY2RqCeIj9SaM6MkkrN&amp;index=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DG53uVamqOd0%26list%3DPLxWYT0p5UiNeoAPY2RqCeIj9SaM6MkkrN%26index%3D1&d=hKO5vKCyTOC8%2FV9T1xBu14RM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=7f1b3a0e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G53uVamqOd0&amp;list=PLxWYT0p5UiNeoAPY2RqCeIj9SaM6MkkrN&amp;index=1</a>"},{"pid":"9657a89dac644e486a0afd6490963cb0ce996b3d","tid":1017693,"uid":55800,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T16:29:57.000Z","msg":"我覺得佢首問題青年仲正，始終callstar出身嘅佢都係唱返社會歌比較適合，可惜因為唔係情歌所以咁後先plug<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/i2gf5J3v0iM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fi2gf5J3v0iM&d=hKO5vKCyTOC8%2FV9T1xBu14RM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=500abcde\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/i2gf5J3v0iM</a>"},{"pid":"a1f0a5ac39c44edcd380fb175b059db8ec88daa6","tid":1017693,"uid":166992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T16:35:38.000Z","msg":"有"},{"pid":"ab836840ab41dd508d21152b1368ef439c72f8c8","tid":1017693,"uid":160589,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T18:06:55.000Z","msg":"今年隻碟幾好 我見都幾多人買"},{"pid":"c